{
  "texts": [
    "The toolbox is built on top of the following well established, documented and maintained Python package dependencies: NumPy (https://numpy.",
    "org; [62] [63] [64]), SciPy (https://scipy.org; 65), pandas (https://pandas.pydata.",
    "org; 66), Scikit-Learn (https://scikit-learn.org; 67), Gym (https://www.",
    "gymlibrary.dev; 68), NeuroGym (https://neurogym.github.io; 53), ReservoirPy (https://github.com/reservoirpy/reservoirpy; 69), bctpy (https://github.com/aestrivex/bctpy; 70), Seaborn (https://seaborn.",
    "pydata.org; 71) and Matplotlib (https://matplotlib.org; 72)."
  ]
}